Common Questions

Is the career assessment really free?

Absolutely free! The complete career code assessment is 100% free with no hidden costs. We believe career guidance should be accessible to everyone.

As we're just starting out, we appreciate any feedback to help us improve!

How does the career matching work?

Our unique algorithm analyzes your personality type, passion domains, and work preferences to generate a personalized career code. This code matches against our database of 110+ carefully researched careers.

We're continuously refining our system - your feedback helps us improve accuracy!

Can I retake the assessment?

Yes! You can retake it as many times as you like. Your career code might evolve as your interests and preferences change over time.

Different answers = different codes = different career suggestions!
